                        CFM London Minutes</note>
                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">Record of Decisions of the Thirtieth Meeting of the
                            Council of Foreign Ministers, Lancaster House, London, September 30,
                            1945, 9:30 p.m.</hi>
                    </head>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName>London</placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian" when="1945-09-30T21:30:00+00:00">September 30, 1945, 9:30 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <opener>
                        <seg rendition="#left">C.F.M.(P) (45) 30th Meeting</seg>
                    </opener>
                    <p rend="center">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Present</hi>
                    </p>
